import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import alansal as al
import noktasal as no
In [2]:
I = plt.imread("../data/rose.png")[:, :, :3]
I = no.gray_scale(I)

plt.figure(figsize=(14, 8))

plt.subplot(2, 3, 1)
plt.imshow(I)

plt.subplot(2, 3, 4)
plt.hist(I.reshape(-1), bins=256, range=(0, 1))

plt.subplot(2, 3, 2)
J = al.turdeslik(I)
plt.imshow(J)

plt.subplot(2, 3, 5)
plt.hist(J.reshape(-1), bins=256, range=(0, 1))

plt.subplot(2, 3, 3)
L = no.esikleme(J, esik=0.2)
plt.imshow(L)

plt.subplot(2, 3, 6)
plt.hist(L.reshape(-1), bins=256, range=(0, 1))

plt.show()

I = plt.imread("../data/rose.png")[:, :, :3]
I = no.gray_scale(I)
I = no.gurultu_ekle(I, p=0.5)

plt.figure(figsize=(10, 8))

plt.subplot(2, 2, 1)
plt.imshow(I)

plt.subplot(2, 2, 2)
plt.hist(I.reshape(-1), bins=256, range=(0, 1))

plt.subplot(2, 2, 3)
h=np.ones((3, 3), dtype=bool)
J = al.ortanca(I, h=h)
plt.imshow(J)

plt.subplot(2, 2, 4)
plt.hist(J.reshape(-1), bins=256, range=(0, 1))

plt.show()
